WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.260 align:middle line:10%
>> One of the greatest
mysteries of our universe--

00:00:04.260 --> 00:00:06.900 align:middle line:10%
what existed before
the Big Bang,

00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.780 align:middle line:10%
and how was our
universe created?

00:00:09.780 --> 00:00:12.570 align:middle line:84%
Was our universe
created in a lab,

00:00:12.570 --> 00:00:16.620 align:middle line:84%
by a higher form of
extraterrestrial intelligence?

00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:18.660 align:middle line:90%
This is "Gaia News."

00:00:18.660 --> 00:00:21.534 align:middle line:90%
